<bibRefCitation author="Fang, Z. &amp; Tang, C. - T. &amp; Zhu, Y. &amp; Xiong, T. &amp; Sinclair, F. &amp; Hearn, J. &amp; Mikolajczak, K. M. &amp; Melika, G. &amp; Stone, G. N. &amp; Fang, S." box="[467,669,1883,1909]" pageId="32" pageNumber="33" pagination="805 - 820" refId="ref43744" refString="Fang, Z., Tang, C. - T., Zhu, Y., Xiong, T., Sinclair, F., Hearn, J., Mikolajczak, K. M., Melika, G., Stone, G. N. &amp; Fang, S. (2020 b) Lithosaphonecrus edurus Fang, Melika &amp; Tang, a new cynipid inquiline species (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Synergini) from Sichuan, China. Proceedings of the Entomological Society of Washington, 122 (4), 805 - 820. https: // doi. org / 10.4289 / 0013 - 8797.122.4.805" type="journal article" year="2020">
